{"id":1090,"mod":"cs","level":"A2","cat":"Güvenlik","icon":"🦠","word":"Malware","syl":["Mal","ware"],"ph":"/ˈmælweər/","wt":"noun","tr":"Kötü Amaçlı Yazılım","tpl":"The ___ infected the system.","sent":"The <strong>malware</strong> infected the system and stole data.","str":"S+V+O","rel":["Virus","Trojan","Antivirus"],"why":"Malware is the generic term for all malicious software.","da":"My computer is acting strange.","db":"Run an antivirus scan — it might be malware."},
