{"id":1092,"mod":"cs","level":"A2","cat":"Sistem","icon":"⚙️","word":"Process","syl":["Pro","cess"],"ph":"/ˈprəʊses/","wt":"noun","tr":"Süreç","tpl":"Kill the stuck ___.","sent":"Kill the stuck <strong>process</strong> to free up memory.","str":"V+O+Inf [Imp]","rel":["Thread","CPU","Memory"],"why":"Process management is fundamental to operating systems.","da":"My computer is very slow.","db":"Check Task Manager for a stuck process."},
{"id":1093,"mod":"cs","level":"A2","cat":"Sistem","icon":"⚡","word":"Performance","syl":["Per","for","mance"],"ph":"/pərˈfɔːrməns/","wt":"noun","tr":"Performans","tpl":"Optimize the code for better ___.","sent":"Optimize the code to achieve better <strong>performance</strong>.","str":"V+O+Inf [Imp]","rel":["Speed","Optimize","CPU"],"why":"Performance optimization is a valued skill everywhere.","da":"The app loads in 8 seconds.","db":"We need to improve the performance."},
{"id":1094,"mod":"cs","level":"A2","cat":"Sistem","icon":"📝","word":"Log","syl":["Log"],"ph":"/lɒɡ/","wt":"noun/verb","tr":"Kayıt","tpl":"Check the error ___.","sent":"Check the error <strong>log</strong> to find what went wrong.","str":"V+O+Inf [Imp]","rel":["Debug","Monitor","Console"],"why":"Log files are the main debugging source in production.","da":"Something went wrong last night.","db":"Check the log files — they recorded everything."},
{"id":1095,"mod":"cs","level":"A2","cat":"Sistem","icon":"🔒","word":"Permission","syl":["Per","mis","sion"],"ph":"/pərˈmɪʃən/","wt":"noun","tr":"İzin","tpl":"Grant ___ to run the script.","sent":"Grant execute <strong>permission</strong> to run the script.","str":"V+O+Inf [Imp]","rel":["chmod","Root","User"],"why":"File permissions are critical in Linux security.","da":"I cannot run this script.","db":"You need execute permission — run chmod +x."},
{"id":1096,"mod":"cs","level":"A2","cat":"Sistem","icon":"🗂️","word":"Algorithm","syl":["Al","go","rithm"],"ph":"/ˈælɡərɪðəm/","wt":"noun","tr":"Algoritma","tpl":"This ___ sorts the data.","sent":"This sorting <strong>algorithm</strong> runs in O(n log n) time.","str":"S+V+Prep","rel":["Sort","Search","Complexity"],"why":"Algorithm is tested in every tech interview.","da":"How do search engines work so fast?","db":"They use optimized algorithms."},
{"id":1097,"mod":"cs","level":"A2","cat":"Programlama","icon":"🌳","word":"Array","syl":["Ar","ray"],"ph":"/əˈreɪ/","wt":"noun","tr":"Dizi","tpl":"Store values in an ___.","sent":"Store all values in an <strong>array</strong> and loop through them.","str":"V+O+Conj [Imp]","rel":["List","Index","Loop"],"why":"Array is the most fundamental data structure.","da":"I have 50 numbers to store.","db":"Put them in an array."},
{"id":1098,"mod":"cs","level":"A2","cat":"Programlama","icon":"🗂️","word":"Stack","syl":["Stack"],"ph":"/stæk/","wt":"noun","tr":"Yığın","tpl":"A ___ is last in first out.","sent":"A <strong>stack</strong> is LIFO — the last item added is the first removed.","str":"S+V+Definition","rel":["Queue","Push","Pop"],"why":"Stack is a classic data structure question in every interview.","da":"How does the browser back button work?","db":"It uses a stack of visited pages."},
{"id":1099,"mod":"cs","level":"A2","cat":"Yazılım","icon":"🆓","word":"Open Source","syl":["O","pen","Source"],"ph":"/ˈoʊpən sɔːrs/","wt":"adj/noun","tr":"Açık Kaynak","tpl":"Python is ___ software.","sent":"Python is <strong>open source</strong> — anyone can view and contribute.","str":"S+V+Adj","rel":["GitHub","License","Free"],"why":"Open source powers most of the internet.","da":"Who maintains this software?","db":"It is open source — the community maintains it."},
{"id":1100,"mod":"cs","level":"A2","cat":"Yazılım","icon":"🔖","word":"License","syl":["Li","cense"],"ph":"/ˈlaɪsəns/","wt":"noun","tr":"Lisans","tpl":"You need a ___ to use this.","sent":"You need a valid <strong>license</strong> to use this software legally.","str":"Modal+N+Inf","rel":["Copyright","Open Source","Legal"],"why":"Software licensing is a legal topic every IT professional faces.","da":"Can I share this software with others?","db":"Only if the license allows it."},

