{"id":1129,"mod":"cs","level":"B1","cat":"Güvenlik","icon":"🕵️","word":"Vulnerability","syl":["Vul","ner","a","bil","i","ty"],"ph":"/ˌvʌlnərəˈbɪlɪti/","wt":"noun","tr":"Güvenlik Açığı","tpl":"Patch the ___ immediately.","sent":"Patch the <strong>vulnerability</strong> before attackers find it.","str":"V+O+Adv [Imp]","rel":["Patch","Exploit","Security"],"why":"Finding vulnerabilities is the core job of security engineers.","da":"Is our system safe?","db":"Run a scan — there might be vulnerabilities."},
