{"id":1149,"mod":"cs","level":"B1","cat":"Veri","icon":"📊","word":"Data Structure","syl":["Da","ta","Struc","ture"],"ph":"/ˈdeɪtə ˈstrʌktʃər/","wt":"noun","tr":"Veri Yapısı","tpl":"Choose the right ___ for the problem.","sent":"Choose the right <strong>data structure</strong> for the best performance.","str":"V+O+Prep [Imp]","rel":["Array","Stack","Tree"],"why":"Data structures is the most important CS course.","da":"When should I use an array vs a list?","db":"It depends on the use case — that is data structures."},
{"id":1150,"mod":"cs","level":"B1","cat":"Web","icon":"🔒","word":"SSL Certificate","syl":["S","S","L","Cer","tif","i","cate"],"ph":"/ˌɛsɛsˈɛl səˈtɪfɪkɪt/","wt":"noun","tr":"SSL Sertifikası","tpl":"Install an ___ for HTTPS.","sent":"Install an <strong>SSL certificate</strong> to enable HTTPS on your website.","str":"V+O+Inf [Imp]","rel":["HTTPS","Encryption","Security"],"why":"SSL certificates are required for every modern website.","da":"How do I make my website secure?","db":"Install an SSL certificate — it enables HTTPS."},

